Debugging Memory issues

Techniques :
    1, export MEMORY_CHECK_=3 and run the program (Set it to 0 to disable)
    2, dmalloc, electricfence or valgrind
    3, build and run with -fsanitize=undefined -fsanitize=address
    4, 

